@OrderService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5100

### Create Order - will succeed (PROD-001 has 100 in stock)
POST {{OrderService_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PROD-001",
  "quantity": 5
}

### Create Order - will fail (PROD-999 does not exist)
POST {{OrderService_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PROD-999",
  "quantity": 10
}

### Create Order - will fail (too many items)
POST {{OrderService_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PROD-002",
  "quantity": 999
}

### Get Order by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET {{OrderService_HostAddress}}/orders/{{orderId}}
